          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> grated onion</strong>, <strong>beef mince</strong>,<strong> baharat</strong>, <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>cumin </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a large bowl – this is your<strong> beef mix</strong></p><p><strong>Knead the beef mix </strong>thoroughly with clean hands for 2-3 min (this helps the mixture hold together when cooking), then shape into 6<span class=\"text-danger\"> [12] </span>koftas</p><p>Add the <strong>koftas</strong> to one side of a lightly oiled<strong> baking tray</strong></p>",
