      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong>, <strong>chopped courgette </strong>and the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>to the other side of the tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 12-15 min or until cooked through</p><p>Meanwhile dissolve the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [400ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
