    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the bulgur is cooking, chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks (reserve a few leaves for garnish!)</p><p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Once the bulgur is done, remove the pot from the heat and fluff with a fork</p>",
