      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>roasted veg bulgur </strong>and dollop the <strong>garlic yoghurt </strong>over the top</p><p>Top with the <strong>beef koftas </strong>and garnish with the <strong>reserved parsley leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
